Brahmacharini Mata Aarti With Lyrics:-
जय ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ मैया 
जय ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ 
अपने भक्त जनो पे 
अपने भक्त जनो पे 
करती सदा दया 
ॐ जय ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ 
दर्शन अनुपम मधुरम 
साधना रत रहती 
माँ साधना रत रहती
शिव जी की आराधना 
शिव जी की आराधना 
मैया सदा करती 
ॐ जय ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ 

बाए हाथ कमंडल 
दाहिने में माला 
है दाहिने में माला
रूप ज्योतिर्मय अद्भुत
रूप ज्योतिर्मय अद्भुत 
सुख देने वाला 
ॐ जय ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ 

देव ऋषि मुनि साधु 
गुण माँ के गाते 
है गुण माँ के गाते
शक्ति स्वरूपा मैया 
शक्ति स्वरूपा मैया 
सब तुमको ध्याते 
ॐ जय ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ 

संयम तप वैराग्य 
प्राणी वो पाता 
है प्राणी वो पाता
ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ को 
ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ को 
जो निसिदिन ध्याता 
ॐ जय ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ 

नव दुर्गा में मैया 
दूजा तुम्हारा स्वरूप 
माँ दूजा तुम्हारा स्वरूप
श्वेत वस्त्र धारिणी माँ 
श्वेत वस्त्र धारिणी माँ 
ज्योतिर्मय तेरा रूप 
ॐ जय ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ 

दूजे नवरात्रे मैया 
जो तेरा व्रत धारे
माँ जो तेरा व्रत धारे
करके दया जग जननी 
करके दया जग जननी 
तू उसको तारे 
ॐ जय ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ 

शिव प्रिय शिवा ब्रह्माणी 
मैया दया कीजे
मेरी मैया दया कीजे
बालक है हम तेरे 
बालक है हम तेरे 
चरण शरण लीजे
ॐ जय ब्रह्मचारिणी माँ 

करुणा हमपे दिखाओ 
ब्रम्हाणी माता 
है ब्रम्हाणी माता 
महिमा तेरी जो गाये 
महिमा तेरी जो गाये

Kaffara Episode 73 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 3rd October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

Namo Namo Ambe Dukh Harni
Nirakar Hai Jyoti Tumhari
Tihun Lok Phaili Ujiyari

Shashi Lalaat Mukh Maha Vishala
Netra Lal Bhrikouti Vikarala
Roop Maatu Ko Adhik Suhave
Darsh Karat Jan Ati Sukh Paave
Tum Sansar Shakti Ley Keena
Palan Hetu Anna Dhan Deena
Annapoorna Hui Jag Paala
Tumhi Aadi Sundari Bala

Pralayakal Sab Nashaan Haari
Tum Gouri Shiv Shankar Pyari
Shiv Yogi Tumhare Gun Gaavein
Brahma Vishnu Tumhein Nit Dhyaave
Roop Saraswati Ko Tum Dhara
De Subuddhi Rishi Munina Ubara
Dhara Roop Narsimha Ko Amba
Pragat Bhayi Phaad Kar Khamba

Raksha Kari Prahlad Bachayo
Hiranyaykush Ko Swarg Pathayo
Lakshmi Roop Dharo Jag Mahin
Shree Narayan Anga Samahin

Ksheer Sindhu Mein Karat Vilaasa
Daya Sindhu Deejey Mann Aasa
Hingalaja Mein Tumhi Bhawani
Mahima Amit Na Jaat Bakhani

Matangi Dhoomawati Mata
Bhuvaneshwari Bagala Sukhdata
Shree Bhairav Tara Jag Tarini
Chhinna Bhala Bhava Dukh Nivarini
Kehari Vahan Sohe Bhawani
Laangur Veer Chalat Agavani
Kar Mein Khappar Khadaga Virajay
Jako Dekh Kaal Darr Bhajey

Sohe Astra Aur Trishula
Jate Uthata Shatru Hiya Shoola

Nagkoti Mein Toumhi Virajat
Tihoun Lok Mein Danka Baajat
Shumbh Nishumbh Daanav Tum Maare
Rakta Beej Shankhana Sanghaare
Mahishasur Nrip Ati Abhimani
Jehi Agh Bhar Mahi Akulaani

Roop Karaal Kali Ka Dhara
Sena Sahita Tum Tihin Samhara
Pidh Pari Santana Par Jab Jab
Bhayi Sahay Maat Tum Tab Tab
Amarpuri Auro Sab Lokaa
Tab Mahima Sab Rahey Ashoka
Jwala Mein Hai Jyoti Tumhari
Tumhein Sada Poojey Nar Nari

Prem Bhakti Se Jo Jas Gaave
Dukh Daridra Nikat Nahin Aave
Dhyave Jo Nar Man Layi
Janma Maran Tako Chhouti Jaayi
Jogi Sur Muni Kahat Pukaari
Yog Nahi Bina Shakti Tumhari
Shankar Acharaj Tap Kinho
Kaamaru Krodh Jeet Sab Leenho

Nishdin Dhyan Dharo Shankar Ko
Kaahu Kaal Nahin Sumiro Tumko
Shakti Roop Ko Maram Na Paayo
Shakti Gayi Tab Mann Pachitayo
Sharnagat Huyi Kiriti Bakhai
Jai Jai Jai Jagadambe Bhawani

Bhayi Prasanna Aadi Jagadamba
Dayi Shakti Nahin Keen Vilamba

Maukon Maatu Kashta Ati Ghero
Tum Bin Kaun Hare Dukh Mero
Asha Trishna Nipat Satave
Ripu Murakh Mohi Ati Darpave
Shatru Nash Keejai Maharani
Soumiron Ikchit Tumhein Bhawani
Karo Kripa Hey Maatu Dayala
Riddhi Siddhi Dey Karahou Nihaala

Jab Lagi Jiyoun Daya Phal Paun
Tumharo Jas Mein Sada Sunaun
Durga Chalisa Jo Koi Gaavey
Sab Sukh Bhog Parampad Paave

Devidas Sharan Neej Jaani
Karahun Krupa Jagadambe Bhawani
Karahun Krupa Jagadambe Bhawani

Sharanagat Raksha Kare
Bhakt Rahe Nishank
Me Aaya Teri Sharan Mein

Kaffara Episode 74 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 3rd October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

Fresh from my big bro's grand wedding - where 'Next one is you?' became the ultimate question - I'm sharing my journey of self-discovery, financial stability, and growth. In this experimental track, I tried something new for the first time, blending catchy beats, witty rhymes, and a fresh perspective. Relate, laugh, and vibe with me on this anthem to embracing your own timeline!🏃‍♂️❌💍

Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 72 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 2nd October 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

Jethalal struggles to sell his electronics as online markets and malls, with their enticing discounts, continue to dominate the market. Will he be able to find a solution to overcome these challenges?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Episode 4206: Discount Dilemma
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal struggles to sell his electronics as online markets and malls, with their enticing discounts, continue to dominate the market. Will he be able to find a solution to overcome these challenges?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

#vratkakhana #navratri #faralirecipes 

Ingredients for Falahari Steamed Nashta
समा के चावल - Sama rice - 3/4 cup (150 grams)
घी - Ghee  - 1 tsp
सेंधा नमक - Rock salt - 1/3 tsp
For Stuffing
आलू - Potato(boiled) - 3 no (250 grams)
सेंधा नमक - Rock salt - 1/2 tsp
काली मिर्च - Black pepper - 1/3 tsp, crushed
अदरक - Ginger - 1/2 tsp, grated
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 1/4 tsp, chopped
हरा धनिया - Coriander - 3-4 tbsp
नींबू का रस - Lemon juice - 1 tsp
For Frying
घी - Ghee  - 1 tsp
जीरा - Cumin seeds - 1/2 tsp
सेंधा नमक - Rock salt - 1 pinch
काली मिर्च - Black pepper - 1 pinch
हरा धनिया - Coriander

……………………………………………….Legends League Cricket

Legends League Cricket is dedicated to cricket lovers and is a pioneer in offering a platform where retired cricket players can demonstrate their skills,
engage with fans, and sense the thrill of cricket once again. The league is dedicated to bring cricket enthusiasts from all walks of life together to celebrate this exciting sport. 
At Legends League Cricket, there are two distinctive cricketing formats being played: Regional and Franchise. Each format gives the game its own charm and competitiveness,
providing players and fans with a combination of exciting encounters. 

Legends League Cricket introduced its global format, LLC Masters in 2022 in an effort to push the limits of cricketing excellence. Its inaugural season was hosted by
Muscat, Oman, and the most recent season was hosted by Doha, Qatar. The three teams that compete in this format to showcase the best of talent: Indian Maharajas,
Asia Lions, and World Giants. Representing the nation’s cricket-crazy culture, India Maharajas bring together the best Indian talent. Asia Lions represent the cricketing
powerhouses of Asia. And, a fiery blend of international talent makes up the team of World Giants. 

Current Teams:
Manipal Tigers, Toyam Hyderabad, Southern Superstars, India Capitals, Konark Suryas Odisha, Gujarat Greats
Absolute Legends Sports Pvt. Ltd. is the owner and operator of Legends League Cricket. It aspires to create a cricket community where legendary players from around the
world come once again to compete and inspire. The new season of Legends League Cricket will be happening in India from 20th September to 16th October. Legends League Cricket
reinvents passion for cricket, sportsmanship, and competition. Let’s celebrate the spirit of cricket together!

……………………………………………….Legends League Cricket

Legends League Cricket is dedicated to cricket lovers and is a pioneer in offering a platform where retired cricket players can demonstrate their skills,
engage with fans, and sense the thrill of cricket once again. The league is dedicated to bring cricket enthusiasts from all walks of life together to celebrate this exciting sport. 
At Legends League Cricket, there are two distinctive cricketing formats being played: Regional and Franchise. Each format gives the game its own charm and competitiveness,
providing players and fans with a combination of exciting encounters. 

Legends League Cricket introduced its global format, LLC Masters in 2022 in an effort to push the limits of cricketing excellence. Its inaugural season was hosted by
Muscat, Oman, and the most recent season was hosted by Doha, Qatar. The three teams that compete in this format to showcase the best of talent: Indian Maharajas,
Asia Lions, and World Giants. Representing the nation’s cricket-crazy culture, India Maharajas bring together the best Indian talent. Asia Lions represent the cricketing
powerhouses of Asia. And, a fiery blend of international talent makes up the team of World Giants.

Manipal Tigers, Toyam Hyderabad, Southern Superstars, India Capitals, Konark Suryas Odisha, Gujarat Greats
Absolute Legends Sports Pvt. Ltd. is the owner and operator of Legends League Cricket. It aspires to create a cricket community where legendary players from around the
world come once again to compete and inspire. The new season of Legends League Cricket will be happening in India from 20th September to 16th October. Legends League Cricket
reinvents passion for cricket, sportsmanship, and competition. Let’s celebrate the spirit of cricket together!

snippet.title: Squid Game: Season 2 | You’re Invited | Netflix
snippet.description:
You're invited to get back in the game.

Season 2 on December 26, 2024.

Only on Netflix.

More Info on Squid Game Season 2:
Three years after winning Squid Game, Player 456 gave up going to the states and comes back with a new resolution in his mind. Gi-hun once again dives into the mysterious survival game, starting another life-or-death game with new participants gathered to win the prize of 45.6 billion won.

Director Hwang Dong-hyuk, who made history at the 74th Primetime Emmys® becoming the first Asian to win Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series, once again helms the series as director, writer, and producer. Lee Jung-jae, Lee Byung-hun, Wi Ha-jun, and Gong Yoo reprise their roles from Season 1 with an impeccable list of new cast members including Yim Si-wan, Kang Ha-neul, Park Gyu-young, Lee Jin-uk, Park Sung-hoon, Yang Dong-geun, Kang Ae-sim, Lee David, Choi Seung-hyun, Roh Jae-won, Jo Yu-ri, and Won Ji-an rounding out the ensemble of colorful characters in the new season.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81203480

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 278 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Squid Game: Season 2 | You’re Invited | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

Heralding the return of the worldwide hit, a new chapter unfolds as Gi-hun comes back with an agenda, having given up on leaving for the US.

रूप अलौकिक पावन रूप अलौकिक पावन  
शुभ फल की दाता जय शैलपुत्री माता

हाथ त्रिशूल कमल दल मैया के साजे मेरी मैया के साजे
शीश मुकुट शोभामयी शीश मुकुट शोभामयी 
मैया के साजे जय शैलपुत्री माता 

दक्षराज की कन्या शिव अर्धांगिनी तुम माँ शिव अर्धांगिनी तुम ।
तुम ही हो सती माता तुम ही हो सती माता 
पाप विनाशिनी तुम जय शैलपुत्री माता 

वृषभ सवारी माँ की सुन्दर अति पावन है सुन्दर अति पावन 
सोभागयशाली बनता सोभागयशाली बनता 
जो करे नीत दर्शन जय शैलपुत्री माता 

आदि अनादि अनामय तुम माँ अविनाशी माँ तुम हो अविनाशी 
अटल अनत अगोचर अटल अनत अगोचर 
अज आनंद राशि जय शैलपुत्री माता 

नौ दुर्गाओं में मैया प्रथम तेरा स्थान मैया प्रथम तेरा स्थान 
रिद्धि सिद्धि पा जाता रिद्धि सिद्धि पा जाता 
जो धरता तेरा ध्यान जय शैलपुत्री माता 

प्रथम नवराते जो माँ व्रत तेरा धारे माँ व्रत तेरा धारे 
कर दे कृपा उस जन पे कर दे कृपा उस जन पे 
तू मैया तारे जय शैलपुत्री माता ।।
 
मूलाधार निवासिनी हम पे कृपा करना माँ हम पे कृपा करना 
लाल तुम्हारे ही हम लाल तुम्हारे ही हम 
दृष्टि दया रखना जय शैलपुत्री माता 

करुणा मई जग जननी दया नजर कीजे माँ दया नजर कीजे 
शिव सती हे मैया शिव सती हे मैया 
चरण शरण लीजे जय शैलपुत्री माता

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the episodes of 'Jo Jetha Wahi Sikander' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cTWbYoG3SaD_hKNC0g53ugi
